com/fenlei/hongzaoguiyuan/" target="_blank">桂圆</a>5个 / 白胡椒粒10g</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wq5dp/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img alt="别人斜杠青年，我有“斜杠排骨”～" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/03/5fc87dd41a1992917.gif_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wq5dp/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img alt="别人斜杠青年，我有“斜杠排骨”～" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/03/5fc87dd4214166799.png_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"> 1 </p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">锅中加入姜片、葱段；将剁开的排骨冷水下锅，焯水捞出备用。</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wq5dp/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img alt="别人斜杠青年，我有“斜杠排骨”～" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/03/5fc87dd42495b9420.gif_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"> 2 </p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">将焯水后的排骨放入锅中，放入盐、花椒、姜片、葱段、花椒面、八角、红枣、枸杞、桂圆、白胡椒粒，加水煮；水开后加入海带，煮好后捞出排骨。<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wq5dp/pic_8/' target='_blank'><img alt="别人斜杠青年，我有“斜杠排骨”～" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/03/5fc87dd4837606380.gif_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wq5dp/pic_9/' target='_blank'><img alt="别人斜杠青年，我有“斜杠排骨”～" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/03/5fc87dd48cf172790.gif_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"> 3 </p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">另起锅倒油，放入煮好的排骨，煎至两面金黄。<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wq5dp/pic_10/' target='_blank'><img alt="别人斜杠青年，我有“斜杠排骨”～" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/03/5fc87dd4bad3a6326.gif_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"> 4 </p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">随即撒上辣椒面、孜然面、花椒面、白芝麻；再加入洋葱粒、蒜末、青椒粒、红椒粒翻炒均匀即可出锅～</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wq5dp/pic_11/' target='_blank'><img alt="别人斜杠青年，我有“斜杠排骨”～" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/03/5fc87dd543a153361.gif_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a99wq5dp/pic_12/' target='_blank'><img alt="别人斜杠青年，我有“斜杠排骨”～" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/03/5fc87dd5bc6e22994.gif_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">一份是鲜香的排骨汤<br/></p><p itemprop="description">一份是酥脆的孜然排骨</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">来唠唠</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">你们喜欢怎么吃排骨？</p><p itemprop="description">留言和大家分享吧~</p>
