<h2 id="cl_0">商品介绍</h2><p itemprop="description">最近入手的小虎队倚天屠龙卡复刻版。</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k43073/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/03/5fc83cc12658f7750.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="赠送了集卡册"/></a>赠送了集卡册</span></p><h2 id="cl_1">外观展示</h2><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k43073/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/03/5fc83d21a08e34114.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="画风和天龙八部卡很像"/></a>画风和天龙八部卡很像</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k43073/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/03/5fc83d226ffa49539.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="背面也像"/></a>背面也像</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k43073/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/03/5fc83d235de327206.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="帅！"/></a>帅！</span></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k43073/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img alt="宝刀屠龙，号令天下，倚天不出，谁与争锋！小虎队倚天屠龙卡晒单" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/03/5fc83d25326e49557.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k43073/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/03/5fc83d268236c9408.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="细节很好"/></a>细节很好</span></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k43073/pic_8/' target='_blank'><img alt="宝刀屠龙，号令天下，倚天不出，谁与争锋！小虎队倚天屠龙卡晒单" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/03/5fc83d27670e68632.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k43073/pic_9/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/03/5fc83d29cadda5079.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="画风统一"/></a>画风统一</span></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k43073/pic_10/' target='_blank'><img alt="宝刀屠龙，号令天下，倚天不出，谁与争锋！小虎队倚